name: Saheed Osupa
description: '''Akorede Babatunde Okunola''' {{IPAc-en||audio=Yo-Saheed Osupa.ogg }} (born 7 August 1970), also known by the stage names '''Saheed Osupa''' or '''King Saheed Osupa'' (''K.S.O.'''), is a [[Nigerian]] [[Fuji music|Fuji]], [[Nigerian musicians|musician]], film actor, and hip Fuji creator.
